snippet.title: Cosmochoria - April 27, 2015 - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Launching April 27th on Steam & Humble Bundle ($9.99 USD), a tiny naked cosmonaut must revive a dying galaxy one seed at a time.

Cosmochoria is a love letter to old-school action / arcade games like Asteroids, Mario Bros. and Sinistar. Cosmochoria is a mesmerizing way to kill hours: hopping between planets, unravelling forgotten mysteries, killing aliens and planting seeds to sprout new life across a long-barren galaxy.

Website: http://www.cosmochoria.com/
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/293240
Humble Store: https://www.humblebundle.com/store/p/cosmochoria_storefront

Trailer Credits...
Trailer By: https://www.youtube.com/user/TenguDrop
Music By: http://mantrakid.bandcamp.com
Featuring: http://ilkae.bandcamp.com
